===[[Season 2]]===
[[Image:Wildfire explosion.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Stannis's fleet is destroyed on Blackwater Bay.]]
The fleet of [[Stannis Baratheon]] sails into Blackwater Bay as a prelude to an attack on King's Landing. [[Tyrion Lannister]] destroys part of the fleet with [[wildfire]], but this only manages to delay the landing of a significant number of Stannis' troops, triggering the [[Battle of the Blackwater]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Blackwater (episode)|Blackwater]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
